---
title: Middle Eastern Lamb & Feta Tacos with Radish Salad, Cucumber & Tahini Yoghurt
description: We’ve always loved a twist on a taco, and this might be one of our best creations yet. Let’s borrow the flavours of the Middle East,
with honey and chermoula tossed lamb mince, tangy tahini yoghurt and a crumble of creamy feta cheese. We can’t wait!
